SELECT [t].[CommunicationLogId], [t].[ActionItems], [t].[ApologiesName], [t].[AttendeeName], [t].[CaseNo], [t].[ClinicalPresentation], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Date], [t].[Discussion], [t].[MeetingTitle], [t].[MinuteTaker], [t].[Plan], [t].[Status], [t].[Time], [t0].[CommunicationLogAttendeesId], [t0].[AttendeesId], [t0].[CommunicationLogId], [t1].[CommunicationLogApologiesId], [t1].[ApologiesId], [t1].[CommunicationLogId]
FROM [tbl_CommunicationLog] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [tbl_CommunicationLogAttendees] AS [t0] ON [t].[CommunicationLogId] = [t0].[CommunicationLogId]
LEFT JOIN [tbl_CommunicationLogApologies] AS [t1] ON [t].[CommunicationLogId] = [t1].[CommunicationLogId]
